{"tid":2207177,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警指拘陳虹秀因「講嘢」播片僅聞籲警冷靜","createTime":"2020-09-18T04:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T04:08:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4d81f593938c848a188ede177a4cabcf4851c93d","tid":2207177,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:08:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/UQ4JMYB4Z5ET7BDTIKYV752GAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FUQ4JMYB4Z5ET7BDTIKYV752GAM%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdW8HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=05974109\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FUQ4JMYB4Z5ET7BDTIKYV752GAM%2F&h=3e555fdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/UQ4JMYB4Z5ET7BDTIKYV752GAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警指拘陳虹秀因「講嘢」播片僅聞籲警冷靜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xMI030xPuEcHoRrnEC6mBysv2G0=/1327x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4MIT3R5675DU5MOCMSXCYEJQYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxMI030xPuEcHoRrnEC6mBysv2G0%3D%2F1327x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4MIT3R5675DU5MOCMSXCYEJQYQ.jpg&h=831191f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳虹秀昨應訊後離開法院。<br />\n<br />\n【8.31暴動案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8.31港島警民衝突，包括「陣地社工」陳虹秀在內八人被控。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作供後由同袍護送兜路走<br />\n<br />\n負責拘捕陳虹秀的警員6798林上嵐昨完成作供後，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林在庭上稱，當晚隨防暴警由金鐘往銅鑼灣方向推進，晚上7時45分見陳站在西行線，向警方說「保持克制」；及後他繼續沿東行線推進，於8時15分在灣仔馬師道再次見陳「同警方講嘢」，遂上前拒捕她。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5klWXHZgSOicCWcinlhnoL2QfI4=/636x813/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HXZL7F3ACBDRFPQVAWDUIHXNMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5klWXHZgSOicCWcinlhnoL2QfI4%3D%2F636x813%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHXZL7F3ACBDRFPQVAWDUIHXNMU.jpg&h=a462cbf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警長黃子誠被指拾棍插贓。<br />\n<br />\n庭上播放《蘋果日報》直播片段，顯示現場嘈吵並傳來連續多下「嘭嘭嘭」疑似槍聲；坐在主控身後的一名女警即吩咐播片男警「細聲啲」。及後片段拍到陳大聲要求警方保持克制，向警方呼籲「你冇生命危險，你係唔需要開任何布袋彈槍」。<br />\n<br />\n本案作供警員沒獲法庭頒匿名令，控方昨一反常態，拒核實證人姓名寫法，稱接獲警方反映，指控傳媒前日報道被指插贓的警長黃子誠後，導致他被起底，故反對控方向傳媒確認姓名寫法。<br />\n<br />\n此外，負責撿取第四被告龔梓舜（23 歲）背包等證物的警長黃子誠昨早續接受盤問，前天他否認從地上拾起伸縮棍並放入被告背囊插贓，辯方昨播片，拍到一名戴黃帽男子跑過並跌了一支棍落地，該棍滾至行人路旁，被一個盒「冚住」。黃同意，但究竟在他拾起該棍狀物前有沒有人碰過該盒，他稱「不肯定」。當辯方再播片後黃改口「同意」，但澄清「冚住電筒」。辯方稱拾起的是伸縮棍，「執電筒係講大話」，黃否認。聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC12/20"}]}